properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57amsterdamNever got a picture of myself there because....well because i was kinda "messed up" the whole time. You get the picture.

properties.name: Arc de Triomphe
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57Great view of a great (and very clean) city. I got to see Lance Armstrong win his record breaking sixth tour de france.

properties.name: Barcelona, Spain
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57BarcelonaGreat trip to Barcelona and I did a lot of partying. Really fun stuff!

properties.name: Buenos Aires, Argentina
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57One of my favorite trips ever. I met incredibly fun and cool people and had an amazing time. BA is one of the best cities in the world and not many people know about it. I was lucky enough to go when everything was 1/3 the price compared to ours. Incredible! A must go for any world traveler.

properties.name: Cayman Islands
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57We went here for a wedding and it was spectacular. The scuba diving was absolutely amazing and the water was perfect.

properties.name: Empire State Building
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57empire state buildingGreat views and we had a great time in the city. Lots of snow though, it was the most ever recorded that late in March.

properties.name: Iguazu Falls, Argentina
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57Incredible! One of the most amazing landscapes on earth.

properties.name: Laguna Beach
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57  Beautiful place with massive houses. Crazy expensive.

properties.name: Miami Beach
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57  Miami BeachWe went to the Miami Boat show. They were gigantic and made us feel very insignificant.

properties.name: Pamplona, Spain
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57We went to San Fermin (The Running of the Bulls) and it was ridiculous. I\'ve never seen partying like that in my life. We stayed up literally all night drinking and then I went and ran with the bulls all the way into the arena. One of the greatest things I (or anyone) could ever experience. If you wanna party go here.

properties.name: Tower Bridge(London Bridge)
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57London, EnglandAnother great trip. We spent the six days in london and still didnt come close to seeing everything. very expensive though and that was in 2004, i can only imagine now.

properties.name: Vail, CO
properties.description: Posted by Dwilli57Great ski trip with lots of snow!
